Migration2
==========

Yet another migartion library for ActiveRecord


Example
=======

class CreateUsers < Special::Migrations::Table
  column :user,       :string
  column :pass,       :string
  column :created_at, :datetime
  column :updated_at, :datetime
end


Special Options
===============

schema   : specify table_name explicitly on defining plural migrations
fallback : one of :none, :log, :error(default)


